  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488470/extras/0e8445c5466a3cc9717cf847b095fc8a.avif?t=1765817822\" width=587 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Politon:</strong> A turn-based strategy game that will push your strategic and management skills to the limit! Expand your territory, strengthen your economy, and outsmart your enemies by planning your strategy carefully.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Unique Experience for Strategy Enthusiasts</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Manage your resources wisely, predict your enemies' moves, and outmaneuver them to achieve victory. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Diverse Game Modes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge opponents in online multiplayer battles or delve into Politon’s story in the single-player campaign. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488470/extras/c98372a2e099365a6855ebba79a4ffec.poster.avif?t=1765817822\" width=622 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488470/extras/c98372a2e099365a6855ebba79a4ffec.webm?t=1765817822\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488470/extras/c98372a2e099365a6855ebba79a4ffec.mp4?t=1765817822\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dynamic World</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a world filled with evolving threats and opportunities with every move you make.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Forge Your Own Path</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you rely on military power or diplomacy to achieve your goals? The choice is entirely yours!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Politon, strategy is your greatest weapon! Face your rivals and carve your name into history! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488470/extras/3827ef3b3a6b46437de8a2420cc4c35c.poster.avif?t=1765817822\" width=622 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488470/extras/3827ef3b3a6b46437de8a2420cc4c35c.webm?t=1765817822\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488470/extras/3827ef3b3a6b46437de8a2420cc4c35c.mp4?t=1765817822\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488470/extras/0e8445c5466a3cc9717cf847b095fc8a.avif?t=1765817822\" width=587 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Politon:</strong> A turn-based strategy game that will push your strategic and management skills to the limit! Expand your territory, strengthen your economy, and outsmart your enemies by planning your strategy carefully.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Unique Experience for Strategy Enthusiasts</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Manage your resources wisely, predict your enemies' moves, and outmaneuver them to achieve victory. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Diverse Game Modes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge opponents in online multiplayer battles or delve into Politon’s story in the single-player campaign. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488470/extras/c98372a2e099365a6855ebba79a4ffec.poster.avif?t=1765817822\" width=622 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488470/extras/c98372a2e099365a6855ebba79a4ffec.webm?t=1765817822\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488470/extras/c98372a2e099365a6855ebba79a4ffec.mp4?t=1765817822\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dynamic World</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a world filled with evolving threats and opportunities with every move you make.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Forge Your Own Path</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you rely on military power or diplomacy to achieve your goals? The choice is entirely yours!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Politon, strategy is your greatest weapon! Face your rivals and carve your name into history! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488470/extras/3827ef3b3a6b46437de8a2420cc4c35c.poster.avif?t=1765817822\" width=622 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488470/extras/3827ef3b3a6b46437de8a2420cc4c35c.webm?t=1765817822\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488470/extras/3827ef3b3a6b46437de8a2420cc4c35c.mp4?t=1765817822\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
